<emphasis box="[392,396,1856,1879]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Basal leaves lanceolate, acute, the cauline 
<emphasis box="[178,188,1884,1907]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">1</emphasis>
-2, similar or smaller
<emphasis box="[441,445,1884,1907]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Spike 2- to 5-flowered, lax
<emphasis box="[781,785,1884,1907]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Outer perianth-segments 8-10 mm, oblong-ovate to orbicular, purple, pink, green, greenish-purple or whitish; inner 6-8 mm, at least 
<emphasis box="[945,951,139,162]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">1</emphasis>
/2as long as the outer, linear-lanceolate, purple or pink, glabrous
<emphasis box="[953,957,166,189]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Labellum 10-12 x 8-12 mm, orbicular to obovate, velutinous, without basal protuberances, with an appendage, dark purple, rarely brown; speculum horseshoe-shaped, scutelliform, or of 2 parallel lines, in the anterior part of the labellum
<emphasis box="[1551,1555,249,272]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
Connective acute
<emphasis box="[1044,1048,277,300]" pageId="22" pageNumber="347">.</emphasis>
